          <span class="eng-stat-count font-headline font-black text-4xl text-primary tabular-nums" data-count="16">16</span>
          <p class="mt-0.5 font-label text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-on-surface-variant leading-tight">Lavatory Systems</p>
